Hugin macOS Community
=====================

This is an unofficial macOS-focused derivative and distribution project based
on Hugin Panorama Stitcher.

Original project:
  Hugin Panorama Stitcher
  https://hugin.sourceforge.io/
  https://sourceforge.net/p/hugin/hugin/

Copyright in upstream Hugin source code, artwork, translations and documentation
remains with the original authors and contributors. Changes made in this
repository are identified through Git history and release notes.

This project name and presentation must not imply endorsement by the upstream
Hugin maintainers.
